{"tid":176230,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[人類滅絕計劃]馬斯克創立Neuralink 冀開發電腦人腦融合技術","createTime":"2017-03-28T05:09:05.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-28T07:06:50.000Z","uid":77196,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d0658ac8286da370ceb43592ae21364e6bea960f","tid":176230,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T05:09:05.000Z","msg":"《華爾街日報》引述知情人士稱，身兼特斯拉(Tesla)和SpaceX創始人兼行政總裁的馬斯克，創立的這家Neuralink，從事馬斯克所謂的「神經織網」(neural lace)技術開發，<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>向人腦植入微型電極，冀最終可藉此上傳下載思想</strong></span>。<br />\n<br />\n據聽取Neuralink計劃簡報的人士指，馬斯克可能將擔任新公司重要的領導職務。<br />\n<br />\n馬斯克未有回應查詢。<br />\n<br />\n自稱Neuralink聯合創始人的Max Hodak證實，Neuralink已成立，且馬斯克參與其中。Hodak稱，Neuralink仍是個雛形，各種計劃還在確定中，他未有提供進一步細節。Hodak曾創立通過互聯網提供機械人實驗服務的初創公司Transcriptic。<br />\n<br />\n據悉，Neuralink打造的首批產品可能是用於治療癲癇、重度抑鬱症之類腦部頑疾的先進植入物。這類植入物將基於已用於治療柏金遜症之類腦部疾病的較簡單電極。此類疾病治療的市場規模達數十億美元。"},{"pid":"4ba0aee1377af91027568f950976ec3a505ca678","tid":176230,"uid":56453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T05:10:30.000Z","msg":"BIC？<br />\nBurst Link！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01afff37a92de93170f9584da3136ea0c358c611","tid":176230,"uid":77196,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T05:11:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>BIC？<br />\nBurst Link！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有聲 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"871a651b14da2302f007eb718269f40ac78cdc9b","tid":176230,"uid":52358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T05:20:21.000Z","msg":"NieR Automata"},{"pid":"6ab85c5e0482998c42727c9747faf5d586ea938d","tid":176230,"uid":23023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T07:05:28.000Z","msg":"全身義肢不是夢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n人人都可以係機械人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a062c3c1f26631c0d2a8ee459e3f9379c6e3030","tid":176230,"uid":9191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T07:06:50.000Z","msg":"又係啲電影撚FF貼圖打飛機嘅時候<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}